snippet: Anthony Rendon homered and drove in four runs, Jordan Zimmermann pitched seven shutout innings, and the Washington Nationals routed the Philadelphia Phillies 11-0 Saturday night....

headline.print_headline: Nationals Bats Come Alive in 11-0 Rout of Phillies
